snippet.title: Best VGM 40 - DuckTales - The Moon
snippet.description:
Check out my remix here: http://youtube.com/watch?v=hn72sqPP5gM

See also:
Best VGM 820 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FrhLXDBP-2Q
Best VGM 1156 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GhFffRvPfig
Best VGM 1314 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Xm7lW0uvFpc

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

NES
Duck Tales
The Moon
